00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,520
Slip of the tongue. He's also surnamed Jin.

293
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,360
We should

294
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,520
fight against evil forces

295
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,000
and build a new Binhai.

296
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,000
- Right.
- Cheers!

297
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,840
They've drunk it up.

298
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,640
Come on, drink up!

299
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,360
Bottoms up!

300
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,280
- Come on.
- This...

301
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,560
What is this?

302
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,480
It's homemade.

303
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,720
Tonic wine.

304
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,280
This wine is strong.

305
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,590
You should drink it slowly.

306
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,520
Being strong is fine.

307
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,490
My brother can handle it.

308
00:10:36,490 --> 00:10:37,960
Come on, bottoms up!

309
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:39,960
Impressive!

310
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,080
Very impressive!

311
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,240
Good capacity!

312
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,120
Mr. Jin, good capacity!

313
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,840
- How is it?
- Great!

314
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:49,920
How about some beer?

315
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,480
- Sure.
- Yeah, have some beer.

316
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,280
Bye.

317
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:01,380
(Binhai Town Market)

318
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,840
It's finally over.

319
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:10,340
It was a misunderstanding.

320
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,920
It's so quiet here.

321
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,240
Right.

322
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,200
Here,

323
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,400
there's no city noise or fast pace.

324
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,880
Actually,

325
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,480
living here

326
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,800
is pretty nice.

327
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,360
Of course.

328
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,600
Life here is simple,

329
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,080
but it has a kind

330
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,320
of rare tranquility

331
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,240
and contentment.

332
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,920
In the city,

333
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,800
it's always hectic,

334
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,320
leaving no room to breathe.

335
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,120
But here,

336
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,400
time seems to slow down.

337
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:26,430
