338
00:12:27,950 --> 00:12:31,460
♪Who lied to escape judgment?♪

339
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:34,760
♪How to settle this all?♪

340
00:12:35,450 --> 00:12:39,720
♪Lingering entanglements,
each shining bright♪

341
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:44,780
♪Some answers remain unspoken♪

342
00:12:48,070 --> 00:12:53,160
♪I was lucky to have a long bond♪

343
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:58,450
♪To say I like you is too late♪

344
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:01,540
♪Thinking back to when we first met♪

345
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,230
♪My palms were sweaty♪

346
00:13:04,230 --> 00:13:06,550
♪You deeply attracted me♪

347
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:12,570
♪Missing ten years for regretful reunion♪

348
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:19,430
♪I suddenly realized love was deeply buried♪

349
00:13:19,660 --> 00:13:26,350
♪Recalling your laughter and tears♪

350
